        %h5 Date
        %p.light
          The Chaos Cologne conference will open on Friday 15 May, 20:00h with a keynote by Cornelia Sollfrank, net art pioneer, followed by two days of workshops, talks, games and performance on Saturday 16 and Sunday 17 May, 2015.
    .row
      .col.s12
        %h5 Location
        :markdown
          {: .light}
          The conference will take place at the Academy of Media Arts Cologne (Kunsthochschule für Medien / KHM).
          The KHM as an art school brings together practice, theories and reflections. It creates a special experimental climate for independent, artistic work.  Between media, around media, or without being defined by any medium in particular, the KHM combines perspectives, methods, research and ‘thinking practises’.
          For more info please see <http://www.khm.de>.

    .row
